# ⚠️  mt5-executor CANNOT run inside Docker / Linux
#
# MetaTrader5 is a Windows-only native library.
# This service must run directly on the Windows EC2 host.
#
# To start the server on Windows EC2, use:
#   .\start.ps1
# or:
#   python -m uvicorn main:app --host 0.0.0.0 --port 8000
#
# See start.ps1 for the recommended startup method.